{"title":"忆澜波","authors":["杨达"],"dates":[{"year":1984,"month":3,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"忆澜波"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨达"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忍看神州竟陆沉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书生报国有丹心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皈依马列求真理，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"格斗顽凶献此忱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窑洞门前延水滨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨家岭上记犹新。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年不羡神仙侣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白首茕然余热身。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四十余年死与生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万千里路雨还晴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新安江上水和泪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿水青山更可亲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"音容一别两周年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜有新词慰九泉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"君若有知应含笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神州此日百花妍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（遵澜波遗嘱，骨灰撒入新安江水电站水库中。）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}